race.comment: PEPPER PIE (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 350m behind Negative Nibbs (20.11) in a Maiden. Was in the money prior to that. Better than last start and worth following up. HAVING A LOOK (8) produced a moderate run last time when fourth at this track over 350m behind Whistling By (20.16). Key player if finds best. ESPECIAL KIANI (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at Shepparton over 390m behind Barooga King (23.15) in a Maiden. Should be in this for a long way. REBEL SAL (3) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.
